# Sprint 1 cycle-3 fixture (paper §4 tree-mask end-to-end wiring).
#
# Pins the decorator-to-codegen wiring: bare `@tree_mask` alongside
# `@flash_attention` must reach `FlashAttentionConfig::tree_mask=true`,
